                    <div class="exc-description">
                        <p><span style="font-weight: 400;">For most of us, calves are those annoying muscles at the back of our legs that we canât quite seem to grow. Some of us blame our genetics, while others just donât <a href="https://www.endomondo.com/exercise/dumbbell-leg-workout" target="_blank" rel="noopener">train our legs</a>.</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">Whatever your calf size, thereâs no denying the power of strong calves. They support our bodies and help support our daily movements.</span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">The dumbbell standing calf raise forms an essential part of the calf-building formula. In this article, weâve given you everything you need to start growing your calves! </span></p>                    </div>
